e/upload/v1781103134/chitratech-shop/seed/category_tshirt.jpg","linkHref":"/main-product?category=T-Shirt","order":1}],"testimonials":[{"id":"1","text":"The fit feels very flattering and the pieces are easy to mix and match with other items in my wardrobe. Quality that truly lasts.","date":"2 days ago","avatar":"https://res.cloudinary.com/dngbvnleh/image/upload/v1781428964/chitratech-shop/testimonials/f0yk5tr9i0tnhmefk3b5.jpg","rating":4.9,"name":"Mina Gurung"},{"id":"2","text":"The fit feels considered, like it was tailored without the tailor. Minimal branding, maximum quality. Exactly what I wanted.","date":"1 week ago","rating":4.9,"avatar":"https://res.cloudinary.com/dngbvnleh/image/upload/v1781434299/chitratech-shop/testimonials/wnf8dukaoaakznlohnyu.webp","name":"Jenish Shrestha"},{"id":"3","date":"2 weeks ago","text":"I now own three pairs of the trousers. That says everything. The fabric comfort is unmatched in this price range.","avatar":"https://res.cloudinary.com/dngbvnleh/image/upload/v1781429135/chitratech-shop/testimonials/efvsr9bsppyxzzoukno6.jpg","rating":4.9,"name":"Messi"},{"id":"4","rating":4.9,"avatar":"https://res.cloudinary.com/dngbvnleh/image/upload/v1781429116/chitratech-shop/testimonials/wvsd3nil2f0ns1ap3lbi.jpg","date":"3 weeks ago","text":"The fit feels very flattering and the pieces are easy to mix and match with other items in my wardrobe.","name":"Karina"},{"id":"5","text":"The jacket feels modern without being overdone. I can wear it for a smart look during the week and still style it casually on weekends.","date":"1 month ago","rating":4.8,"avatar":"https://res.cloudinary.com/dngbvnleh/image/upload/v1781428919/chitratech-shop/testimonials/hor7f8etiqunk3gc1q8l.jpg","name":"Bhuwan"},{"id":"6","avatar":"https://preview.redd.it/240109-jang-wonyoung-instagram-update-v0-1by307c1xdbc1.jpg?width=1080&crop=smart&auto=webp&s=ee8860eec92f5f578f5b21baad1974370e8dbf9a","rating":4.9,"text":"Every piece feels intentional. The fabric, color, and fit make simple outfits look much more polished.","date":"1 month ago","name":"Wonyoung "}]}}]
